headline: State American Water Announces More Than $200 Million Invested in 2025 Statewide Infrastructure Upgrades
summary: California American Water announced today its 2025 summary of investments for system improvements, totaling more than $200 million in water and wastewater system upgrades throughout its service area across the state.
